        "subject": "LU-12428 tests: robustify 'inactive' option of wait_nm_sync",
        "message": "LU-12428 tests: robustify 'inactive' option of wait_nm_sync\n\nInstead of trying to pass an empty third parameter to wait_nm_sync in\ncase of 'inactive' option, just reset to empty value inside\nwait_nm_sync.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nTest-Parameters: combinedmdsmgs=true mdscount=2 mdtcount=4 osscount=1 ostcount=8 testlist=sanity-sec,sanity-sec,sanity-sec\nTest-Parameters: combinedmdsmgs=true mdscount=2 mdtcount=4 osscount=1 ostcount=8 testlist=sanity-sec,sanity-sec,sanity-sec\nTest-Parameters: combinedmdsmgs=true mdscount=2 mdtcount=4 osscount=1 ostcount=8 testlist=sanity-sec,sanity-sec,sanity-sec\nSigned-off-by: Sebastien Buisson <sbuisson@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: Iaf9894eebc61f07dc65d2669cbb04cd60b424bdf\n"
